---
layout: base.njk
permalink: topics.html
title: "Topics - Jingxiao Cai's Blog"
description: "Browse Jingxiao Cai's technical writing by primary topic."
canonicalPath: "topics.html"
---
<section class="hero hero--compact" aria-labelledby="topics-title">
  <p class="eyebrow">Six reader-oriented paths</p>
  <h1 id="topics-title">Topics</h1>
  <p class="hero__lede">Each post has one primary topic for predictable browsing, while tags preserve the detailed vocabulary.</p>
</section>
<div class="topic-grid topic-grid--archive">
{% for topic in topics %}
  {% set topicPosts = collections.postsByPublished | byTopic(topic.slug) %}
  <a class="topic-card" href="{{ site.basePath }}topics/{{ topic.slug }}.html">
    <span class="topic-card__count">{{ topicPosts.length }} post{% if topicPosts.length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</span>
    <strong>{{ topic.label }}</strong>
    <span>{{ topic.description }}</span>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</div>
